translations.for-more-information-please-visit-our-he:
TERMS AND CONDITIONS

Who is eligible?
*As a NetBet Casino account holder, you’ll be joining our Players Club as a Bronze member from your very first real-money bet (cash balance) played on our games.
How does it work?
* Players Club Points, called NetPoints, will automatically be assigned in real time on every real-money bet (cash) you place on Casino, Live Casino and/or Lotto games.
* Bets made with bonus funds will not count towards Players Club NetPoints.
* Most of our Casino, Live Casino and Lotto games contribute to our NetPoints program.
* More details on the number of points allocated by game categories can be found under the 'EARN NETPOINTS' section.
How and when is my Player Status calculated?
* Your Player Status will be upgraded in real time according to the points required to reach that level. More details on your Players Club Status and the number of points each level requires can be found in the 'PLAYERS CLUB' section.
* Player statuses are reviewed monthly at the start of each month based on the past calendar month (from the first to the last day of ach month) and you must reach the current level point requirement to retain and renew your status for one more month, otherwise you’ll be downgraded to the level for which you]ve collected enough points.
* Bronze, Silver, Gold or Diamond Status are granted for one month. For Platinum and Stellar Status, the level eligibility time frame is extended for six months with the minimum points requirement to be completed in the first two months to be maintained. Once you reach the Elite level you will remain Elite for life.
* Total NetPoints balance available to be spent at the shop functions independently from your Player Status points requirement. For example, if you have collected 124,000 points since the 1st of the month and you've spent some of these in the Club Shop, your level will be calculated based on your total monthly points accumulated (124,000) without considering any purchase’s points deduction nor NetPoints boost. Check your 'MY CLUB' section to control your monthly performance and see how many points you need to accumulate to reach the next level.

What benefits can I get from my NetPoints?
* Accumulated NetPoints can be exchanged for a wide range of rewards available in our 'CLUB SHOP'.
* Some items may be restricted by Player Status level. In order to purchase something from the shop, you’ll need to have accumulated enough points to match the NetPoints value plus have reached the minimum level required to unlock selected item.
* Items bought from the shop cannot be exchanged or transferred or refunded after purchase.
* Once successfully purchased, NetPoint costs will be immediately deducted from your total balance and added to your Players account.
* Casino bonuses will automatically be credited to the player’s ‘Available Offers’ section and must be wagered 40 times (40x playthrough) before winnings may be withdrawn.
* Cash prizes will automatically be credited to player’s cash balance and exempt from wagering conditions (free for cash-out).

How about the bonuses?
* Bonus must be wagered 40 times (playthrough x40) before bonus winnings may be converted into cash funds.
* Cash balance may be withdrawn at any time without restriction, except where necessary, to comply with any general regulatory obligations. Please note, any withdrawals requested before the active bonus wagering requirements have been met will result in all bonus money, plus associated pending bonus winnings, being automatically forfeited.
* The maximum amount which can be converted to your Cash Balance (withdrawable) as a result of fulfilling the bonus wagering requirement is €5,000.
* Any bonus winnings exceeding this amount will be forfeited. For example, if you have accumulated bonus funds of €6,500 once the wagering requirement has been fulfilled, a maximum of $5,000 will be converted as cash and the remaining bonus balance will be reset to zero.
* Bonuses are valid for seven days from their date of issue unless explicitly stated otherwise. At the end of this period, all unused bonuses, bonuses where the playthrough has not been completed or any resulting pending winnings will be automatically deducted from the player's account balance.

How about the Vault tokens
* Purchase a token for your chosen pot in the Club Shop and access the Vault page.
* Submit your chosen digits and try to unlock the Vault (or use the random generator).
* Press 'Open' and discover if you've won the cash.
* Unlimited tokens can be purchased.
* You may win up to €5,000 in cash.
* You might also trigger random mystery prizes.
* Among the mystery prizes are NetPoints, cash and bonuses.

How about the Free Spins?
* NetEnt Free Spins to play on the game displayed on the pop-up triggered when you will claim (minimum spin value depending on each game).
* Playtech Free Spins to play on any Age of the gods slots or any Kingdoms Rise slots (see detail on the item), minimum spin value depending on each game.
* Book of Dead Free Spins to play on Book of Dead slot (minimum spin value).
* Free Spins to play within seven days.
* Free Spins winnings must be wagered 40 times (40x playthrough) before bonus winnings may be converted into cash funds.
* All Free Spins need to be played before it can be purchased again. Please play your pending free spins before trying to purchase another Free Spins package.
* NetEnt games are not available in Canada and therefore players from this country are not eligible for NetEnt Free Spins.
* Bonuses are valid for seven days from their issuing date unless explicitly stated otherwise. At the end of this period, all unused bonuses, bonuses where the playthrough has not been completed or any resulting pending winnings will be automatically deducted from the player's account balance.
* Withdrawal requests before wagering requirements that have been met will result in all bonus money plus associated pending bonus winnings being automatically forfeited.

How about the Mystery Box?
* Once purchased, Mystery Box will instantly appear on the screen.
* Click the box to reveal your prize.
* If the widget is not used immediately, it will remain active and ready to be played on the SPECIAL OFFERS section on your account page.
* The Free Spins are credited directly to player's casino account once the widget is used.
* You can win up to 50 Free Spins depending on the box you have purchased.
* Free Spins are playable on a mystery game displayed on the pop-up triggered when you claim (minimum spin value depending on each game).
* Free Spins winnings must be wagered 40 times (40x playthrough) before bonus winnings may be converted into cash funds.

How about the Magic Chip?
* You can win a random number of Free Games up to 100 Free Games depending on your purchased Magic Chip widget.
* Your Free Game will be credited instantly.
* Free Game(s) are only eligible on the Evolution games you will find in the Live Reward game lobby.
* How do I get My Free Game reward?
1- Access the Live Reward lobby.
2- Accept your reward.
3- Play your Free Game(s) on any eligible games from Evolution Gaming.
* Free Games are exempt from wagering conditions, only for playing purposes, and cannot be cashed out.
* Free Games are valid for two days from their date of issue unless explicitly stated otherwise.
* The maximum amount which can be converted to your Cash Balance (withdrawable) as a result of fulfilling the Free Game requirement is previously indicated and specific to each reward. Any winnings exceeding this amount will be forfeited.

What else do I need to know?
* Players Club benefits will expire after 12 months inactivity. Please note, that if you do not log in to your account for a period of 12 months, you will be automatically reverted back to Bronze level and your NetPoints balance, if any, will be forfeited and not refundable.
* Players notified as bonus seekers are only eligible for cash purchases. For more information on bonus seeker statuses, please refer to our General Terms and Conditions point 14.25, 14.26, 14.5.1
* Offer is subject to NetBet Casino's Terms and Conditions.
* NetBet reserves the right to exclude players who participate in the promotion with multiple accounts. Should we have any reason to believe that either an account or group of accounts are operating systematically, e.g. using specific betting techniques or group wagering, NetBet reserves the right to block or permanently close all accounts. In these circumstances, accounts will be automatically excluded from any further participation in the promotion even if they have already begun depositing or wagering for it.
* Where a Player has failed to meet our Anti-Money Laundering or Responsible Gambling requirements, any accrued NetPoints may be witheld until the Player has satisfied our requirements.
* For more information, please visit our Help Centre > Players Club FAQs.
